Name: Barbarella
Description:
Barbarella was stabbed in the chest.

Three weeks later her neighbour [Yancey-Lisa R.](https://tdor.translivesmatter.info/reports/1975/04/06/yancey-lisa-r_san-francisco-california-usa_e114c7b0) was also killed.

Source: The San Francisco Sentinel April 10, 1975.
